communications.communication:
To Whom It May Concern:

Pursuant to the Freedom of Information Act, I hereby request the following records:

All documents mentioning Crass - the English punk band and art collective active since ~1977 ( see https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Crass ).

The requested documents will be made available to the general public, and this request is not being made for commercial purposes.

In the event that there are fees, I would be grateful if you would inform me of the total charges in advance of fulfilling my request. I would prefer the request filled electronically, by e-mail attachment if available or CD-ROM if not.

Thank you in advance for your anticipated cooperation in this matter. I look forward to receiving your response to this request within 20 business days, as the statute requires.

Sincerely,

J Ader

communications.subject: Florida Sunshine Law Request: VSO Deputy - Hanshard (Badge# 7244)
communications.communication:
To Whom It May Concern:

Pursuant to the Florida Sunshine Law, s. 286.011, F.S., I hereby request the following records with regards to Deputy Sheriff Hanshard (VSO)
(Badge# 7244), to the date this request is processed (as the provided time frame):

Full Name and middle initial (to avoid confusion of officers or deputies within Volusia County with the same last name)
Photo or Headshot
Current badge number
Current rank
Unit assignment
Gender
Race
Date of employment
Government email address
Salary
Disciplinary action/Corrective action/Complaints against him, if any.

The requested documents will be made available to the general public, and this request is not being made for commercial purposes.

I also request that, if appropriate, fees be waived as I believe this request is in the public interest.

In the event that there are fees, I would be grateful if you would inform me of the total charges in advance of fulfilling my request. I would prefer the request filled electronically, by e-mail attachment if available or CD-ROM if not.

Thank you in advance for your anticipated cooperation in this matter. I look forward to receiving your response to this request within 5 business days.

Sincerely,

Bailey Pillon
